# FILE: halabAcademy/courseDisplayPage/courseDisplayPage.desc
# ROLE: High-Focus Learning Environment
# ROUTE: /academy/course/:id
# ACCOUNT: All types can view — enrollment requires Student or Business Freelancer account
# THEME: Dark · IDE/player layout · minimal distractions

## DESIGN SYSTEM
- FULL-SCREEN LAYOUT: h-[calc(100vh-72px)] · no outer page padding
- BG: bg-[#070C18] for player · bg-[#0F1828] for sidebar
- BORDER DIVIDER: border-[#1E2D45] between player and sidebar

## 1. WORKSPACE LAYOUT (12-Column Grid)
- COL 9: Video Player area (flex-1)
- COL 3: Curriculum Sidebar (fixed width 300px · scrollable)

## 2. VIDEO PLAYER (COL 9)
- BG: bg-black · rounded-none (full area)
- CUSTOM CONTROLS: backdrop-blur pill bar at bottom of video
  - Play/Pause · Progress bar (indigo fill) · Volume · Speed · Fullscreen
- OVERLAY TOP-LEFT: Lesson ID + Duration + 🔒 if locked (not enrolled)
- INTERACTION: Like/Dislike + Star rating below video

## 3. CURRICULUM SIDEBAR (COL 3)
- COURSE META (top): Level badge + Duration + Language flag
- LESSON LIST: vertical stack
  - Active: border-r-2 border-[#6366F1] · bg-[#6366F1]/10 · text-[#818CF8]
  - Completed: text-[#10B981] + checkmark icon
  - Locked: text-[#4A5D78] + 🔒 icon
- PROGRESS BAR: thin indigo bar across top of sidebar

## 4. BOTTOM TABS (Below Player)
- TABS: 💬 النقاشات · 📎 الموارد · 📝 ملاحظاتي
- DISCUSSIONS: Q&A thread with nested replies
- RESOURCES: PDF/code file list (download triggers +10 XP for students)
- NOTES: private markdown scratchpad per lesson

## 5. XP & COMPLETION
- Finish lesson: +50 XP for student accounts
- Complete full course: +200 XP + course completion badge

## 6. ACCOUNT TYPE IMPACT
- Guest: can preview first lesson only → locked CTA to enroll
- Student: full access after enrollment
- Business (advertiser/vendor): blocked — redirect to student path note
- Admin: full access + floating [✏️ تعديل الدورة] button
